text: "I'm Just Ken" is a song sang by Canadian actor Ryan Gosling for the 2023 movie Barbie. It was written and produced by Mark Ronson and Andrew Wyatt. The song appears on the soundtrack album Barbie the Album. , the song had over 100 million streams on Spotify and over 3 million views on YouTube. It won Best Song at the 29th Critics' Choice Awards and was nominated for Best Song Written for Visual Media at the 66th Annual Grammy Awards. It was nominated for Best Original Song at the 96th Academy Awards. ==References== Category:2023 songs
